text: Colobothea unilineata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1872. It is known from Nicaragua and Panama.BioLib.cz - Colobothea unilineata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1872
title: Colobothea unilineata
